{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"财报收集API服务","description":"\n中国A股、港股财报PDF收集与提取API\n\n## 功能\n\n* **搜索**: 搜索A股和港股上市公司财报\n* **下载**: 下载单个或批量财报PDF\n* **查询**: 查询已下载PDF信息和统计\n* **提取**: 提取PDF中的财务数据、表格和文本\n* **缓存**: 管理提取结果缓存\n\n## 数据源\n\n* A股: 巨潮资讯网 (cninfo.com.cn)\n* 港股: 港交所披露易 (hkexnews.hk)\n        ","version":"1.0.0"},"paths":{"/api/v1/reports/cn/search":{"get":{"tags":["搜索"],"summary":"Search Cn Reports","description":"搜索中国A股上市公司财报\n\n- **stock_code**: 6位数字股票代码 (如: 000001, 600519)\n- **report_type**: 报告类型\n- **max_count**: 最大返回数量 (1-50)\n\n数据源: 巨潮资讯网","operationId":"search_cn_reports_api_v1_reports_cn_search_get","parameters":[{"name":"stock_code","in":"query","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","pattern":"^[0-9]{6}$","description":"6位股票代码","title":"Stock Code"},"description":"6位股票代码"},{"name":"report_type","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"报告类型: annual(年报), semi_annual(半年报), quarterly(季报), all(全部)","default":"annual","title":"Report Type"},"description":"报告类型: annual(年报), semi_annual(半年报), quarterly(季报), all(全部)"},{"name":"max_count","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","maximum":50,"minimum":1,"description":"最大返回数量","default":10,"title":"Max Count"},"description":"最大返回数量"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/APIResponse_Dict_str__Any__"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/reports/hk/search":{"get":{"tags":["搜索"],"summary":"Search Hk Reports","description":"搜索港股上市公司财报\n\n- **stock_code**: 5位数字股票代码 (如: 00700, 01810)\n- **report_type**: 报告类型\n- **max_count**: 最大返回数量 (1-50)\n\n数据源: 港交所披露易","operationId":"search_hk_reports_api_v1_reports_hk_search_get","parameters":[{"name":"stock_code","in":"query","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","pattern":"^[0-9]{5}$","description":"5位股票代码","title":"Stock Code"},"description":"5位股票代码"},{"name":"report_type","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"报告类型: annual(年报), semi_annual(中期报告), quarterly(季报)","default":"annual","title":"Report Type"},"description":"报告类型: annual(年报), semi_annual(中期报告), quarterly(季报)"},{"name":"max_count","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","maximum":50,"minimum":1,"description":"最大返回数量","default":10,"title":"Max Count"},"description":"最大返回数量"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/APIResponse_Dict_str__Any__"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/reports/cn/download":{"post":{"tags":["下载"],"summary":"Download Cn Report","description":"下载单个A股财报PDF\n\n- **stock_code**: 6位股票代码\n- **url**: 从搜索API获取的下载URL\n- **title**: 可选的文件标题","operationId":"download_cn_report_api_v1_reports_cn_download_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Body_download_cn_report_api_v1_reports_cn_download_post"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/APIResponse_Dict_str__Any__"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/reports/cn/batch-download":{"post":{"tags":["下载"],"summary":"Batch Download Cn Reports","description":"批量下载A股财报PDF\n\n自动搜索并下载指定股票的财报","operationId":"batch_download_cn_reports_api_v1_reports_cn_batch_download_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/BatchDownloadRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/APIResponse_Dict_str__Any__"}}}},"422":{"descri